# Web Frontend Rules

- Use shadcn components from `src/components/ui`
- Forms: react-hook-form + Zod schemas from `@frs/shared`
- Data fetching: TanStack React Query
- Mobile-first for Field Lead and Manager screens
- No inline business validation that diverges from shared Zod schemas
